features.name: TrwB_AAD_bind PFAM Type IV secretion-system coupling protein DNA-binding domain

PNP_UDP_1 Catalyzes the irreversible cleavage of the glycosidic bond in both 5'-methylthioadenosine (MTA) and S- adenosylhomocysteine (SAH AdoHcy) to adenine and the corresponding thioribose, 5'-methylthioribose and S-ribosylhomocysteine, respectively
